    "title": "Senior Revenue Manager at Mango Hotels",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Revenue Manager with drive and ambition, Mango Hotels in Dhanbad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Mango Hotels:\nMango Hotels is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Dhanbad, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mango Hotels!",
